<br>
If you are dueling someone with poor resists, you may as well just have fun with them.  Snare+dot, nuke at the end to prevent XP loss if possible.<br>
<br>
<br>
Voice graft always!<br>
<br>
Just some ideas.<br>
<br>
--The Xool<br>
